*
 * Tests if the parent is a parent of child
 * @param {function|object} parent - Instance or Class
 * @param {function|object} child - Instance or Class
 * @returns {boolean} - is parent a parent of child
 * @private
 * @example
 * class A {}
 * class B extends A {}
 * class C extends B {}
 *
 * isParentOf(A, C) // true
 * isParentOf(B, C) // true
 * isParentOf(C, C) // true
 * isParentOf(B, A) // false
